[node name="Label" type="Label" parent="PanelContainer" unique_id=1418007133]
layout_mode = 2
text = "STORY

“Honey, can you grab a few things from the store?”

Those were the last normal words you heard.

What followed was a list so long it defies logic.

Now you’re racing through aisles, stacking your cart beyond its limits. It wobbles.

One wrong move — and everything spills.

This is no longer shopping.

This is survival."
horizontal_alignment = 1
metadata/_edit_group_ = true

